{"tid":2153713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【正視聽】總辭係得，但要通過民主派公投之後決定！","createTime":"2020-08-12T16:45:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T09:24:16.000Z","uid":206080,"like":117,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"8b95c8ae248942de9d9fc9bc790c576d4e8ea43a","tid":2153713,"uid":206080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T16:45:01.000Z","msg":"佢哋始終都係民選議員，冇可能違背選民意見&ldquo;自己&rdquo;作決定。<br />\n正確做法點呢？係應該以公投嘅形式交返比民眾去決定 e.g初選系統<br />\n<br />\n結果如果係支持總辭嘅話，變相更加肯定呢個議會係一個非法嘅議會，咁就可以令國際上知道呢個議會係非法<br />\n<br />\n但如果唔係有民眾去決定支持佢哋總辭嘅話咁會變相佢哋係&ldquo;自我放棄&rdquo;咗民意授權入去議會發聲<br />\n<br />\n如果你話最後結果係唔支持總辭嘅話<br />\n我會話比你哋聽你哋應該要相信我哋自己<br />\n<br />\n如果有更好意見 可以討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d4475d10a6a98811fc23495b4218959af3cb868","tid":2153713,"uid":206080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T16:46:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dabf6a2a20cf3c2321b5d55a37b68be37aa53bb","tid":2153713,"uid":210558,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T16:48:28.000Z","msg":"支持公投"},{"pid":"1ed1f9a6cee7d58932ccdfe9b186a91c801c3f2d","tid":2153713,"uid":206080,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T16:49:40.000Z","msg":"總辭交翻俾民眾決定"},{"pid":"6fc893ab49e7137af77bc68aba442e106f9cbb0e","tid":2153713,"uid":206080,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T16:52:32.000Z","msg":"如果公投當中佢拉人 重好 送子彈俾國際"},{"pid":"8e9f6db5ced3b6e2eb72c6a1515e5c535f4affa3","tid":2153713,"uid":206080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T16:53:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8dd9ee11a06553969e0b4a4ed1f5af01bed473b","tid":2153713,"uid":14478,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T16:53:12.000Z","msg":"做4年零第一日已經冇mandate"},{"pid":"98c5c5e3f5e90a6873389cd92244695891605b68","tid":2153713,"uid":206080,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid